data.description:
**NEW CARPET JUST PUT IN** Welcome to this charming single-story home nestled in the heart of Maricopa! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bath residence offers comfort, style, and modern living all in one. Situated in a serene neighborhood, this home boasts a warm and inviting exterior with a well-maintained front yard and a cozy porch, providing a warm welcome to all who enter.
The kitchen is a true focal point of the home, featuring sleek granite countertops, modern stainless steel appliances, and a convenient center island. The large pantry ensures that all your culinary essentials are neatly organized. Step outside to the low maintenance backyard, where you'll find a covered patio - an ideal setting for alfresco dining and morning coffee. **Home Has Solar**
